  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dda \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dc4\u0dd2 \u0db4\u0dc4\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dad\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dba\u0dcf \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The young man was killed by his friend's knife",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Katiawa Priyankaragama Police said that a person was attacked and killed with a sharp weapon in Katiawa Yaya 07, Pokunugama area of \u200b\u200bEppawala.",
        "A 25-year-old married man named Dinesh Madhusankha Tennakon, resident of Pokunugama, Katiyava Yaya 07, Eppawala, was killed by his best friend. The police say that the murder was done yesterday (27th) at around 7.30 pm. The Priyankaragama police say that the murder was done by Dinesh Madhusankha's best friend, and the killer was arrested within a few hours of the murder. The police say that the killer is a 32-year-old father of three.",
        "The police also said that the killer also stabbed his own wife with a sharp weapon as well as the victim Dinesh Madhusankha.",
        "Sources of Eppavala hospital said that 7-8 stab wounds were found on the body of Dinesh Madhusankha, who was killed, and he was dead when he was taken to the hospital. The hospital sources added that she was transferred to the hospital and her condition is not serious.",
        "According to the police, the incident took place when Dinesh Madhusankha, who was killed, went to the gas station to get fuel for his motorcycle at the request of his best friend, got fuel and returned the motorcycle to his friend's house.",
        "When the deceased came to the house of the person who had been killed, while he was talking to him inside the house, once, Dinesh went to the house of the killer's parents, which is adjacent to the house on the same land, dressed in a cloak and stabbed several places on the body with a sharp weapon in front of the house. The police said that the killer also stabbed one of the hands of the wife of the killer while trying to prevent it.",
        "The Priyankaragama police said that the killer was arrested within 2 hours of the murder, and the questioning of him is still going on. conducts"
      ],
